metadata.name: Urban Saints pt. I
metadata.description:
Urban Saints pt. I is a movie-style poster-inspired artwork, drawing inspiration from and celebrating my photography series of the same name.

It is a way for a broad audience to enjoy being part of the Urban Saints family and is the next best thing after actually purchasing an NFT from the original portrait collection.

Thank you for believing in me and for supporting my artistic expression and journey! Cheers!

Stefan Vasilev
